# Portfolio Rebuild — Next.js 14 + TypeScript + WebGL

## Overview

Migrate Kishore's portfolio from a Vite/React/JSX stack to a **Next.js 14 (App Router) + TypeScript** project with a cinematic design system, WebGL 3D interactivity, and fluid Framer Motion animations. The current neon-green palette will be replaced by a deep obsidian + cyber-blue + neon-violet scheme.

---

