> [!IMPORTANT]
> **3D Model**: The hero section will use a procedurally-generated animated WebGL sphere/particle cloud by default (no external `.glb` model needed). When you have a ZBrush/Blender export ready (`.glb` with Draco compression), drop it in `public/models/` and set the path in `src/data/config.ts`. This keeps the build working immediately.

> [!WARNING]
> The project install requires `npm install` to run — this downloads ~200 MB of packages (Next.js, Three.js, Framer Motion, etc.) and may take 3–5 minutes depending on your internet connection.

