### Phase 3 — Core UI Components

#### [NEW] `src/components/ui/CustomCursor.tsx`
Magnetic custom cursor that morphs on hover over interactive elements.

#### [NEW] `src/components/ui/Navbar.tsx`
Glassmorphism floating navbar with scroll-progress indicator and magnetic nav links.

#### [NEW] `src/components/ui/SectionHeading.tsx`
