---

### Phase 4 — Hero Section (WebGL)

#### [NEW] `src/components/sections/Hero.tsx`
Full-screen hero featuring:
- `<Canvas>` from `@react-three/fiber`
- `<HeroScene />` — animated icosphere with dynamic shader material reacting to mouse coordinates
- `<Environment>` preset + `<EffectComposer>` for bloom + chromatic aberration (via `@react-spring/postprocessing`)
- `<OrbitControls>` with damping tied to mouse delta
- Floating glassmorphism stat cards (`Experience`, `Projects`, `Skills`) with 3D perspective tilt on hover
- Framer Motion staggered text reveal for name + tagline
- Scroll indicator arrow with bounce animation

#### [NEW] `src/components/three/HeroScene.tsx`
Three.js scene graph:
- `IcosphereModel` — custom geometry with displacement shader driven by `useFrame` clock
- `SpotLight` casting real-time shadows
- `PointLight` in cyber-blue + neon-violet
- Draco-ready `useGLTF` hook (falls back to procedural mesh if no `.glb` path configured)

#### [NEW] `src/components/three/ParticleField.tsx`
10,000-point particle system using `BufferGeometry` and a custom vertex shader — particles drift and respond to mouse proximity.

---

### Phase 5 — About Section

#### [NEW] `src/components/sections/About.tsx`
Bento-box grid layout (CSS Grid, 3 columns × 2 rows):
- **Card 1** (2×1): Bio text with staggered word reveal
- **Card 2** (1×1): Animated skill pills
- **Card 3** (1×1): Experience counter with odometer animation
- **Card 4** (1×1): Location card with CSS globe animation
- **Card 5** (1×1): "Currently building" live status badge
Each card: hover → `translateY(-8px)` + `rotateX/Y` perspective shift + glowing gradient border reveal via CSS `::before` pseudo-element animation.

